{"tid":1816601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教協「訴訟及緊急援助基金」協助反修例事件受影響教師","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T02:10:49.000Z","uid":226984,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88bdd6c50c97dbc413a045fae621fdb30daeb362","tid":1816601,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"教協宣布成立「訴訟及緊急援助基金」，為反修例事件中受影響的教師提供法律援助及緊急經濟援助。<br />\n<br />\n教協會長馮偉華表示，自去年6月反修例風波以來，教育界面對前所未有的打壓和挑戰，過百名教師因不同言論和政治立場表態，受到不同程度的投訴，甚至有老師被停職。他希望透過成立基金，支援受影響老師。<br />\n<br />\n馮偉華又說，現時的眾籌形式完全符合會章，教協亦非次作眾籌，所以清楚知道所有要求規限，相信不會有問題。他又說，基金會由教協理事會支援和運作，正尋找知名人士加入基金會，以第三者身份監察，增加公信力。<br />\n<br />\n他又說， 基金會逐一審視申請個案，根據案情嚴重性及緊急情況而定出每宗個案的審批金額。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501704-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501704-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=df17b2da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501704-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5cd3158c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501704-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1664f6779498a5b12ed9c88754dc117a4bbad62e","tid":1816601,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"得過數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a71cc99c7a66ec33b188cd39d017a57910340b1","tid":1816601,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"975139d7ca54999771aeed217655b018326dbf0e","tid":1816601,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36dd66d08b6910b77a5c06da9bdd7c5f3d3633de","tid":